330
00:17:44,481 --> 00:17:45,758
Le bon fils,

331
00:17:46,516 --> 00:17:48,616
celui sur qui on peut tous compter.

332
00:17:50,382 --> 00:17:52,532
Puis vous avez eu ce rêve.
Et...

333
00:17:53,028 --> 00:17:55,065
